s\n\n* **Name resolution** — resolve ENS names to records, addresses, and content hashes\n* **Primary names** — look up primary names for Ethereum addresses\n* **Name token browsing** — explore registered ENS name tokens\n* **Registrar actions** — query registration, renewal, and transfer history\n\n## Getting Started\n\nThe ENSApi is available at the following endpoints:\n\n\u003CCardGroup_1 client:load />\n\n## Quick Example\n\nResolve records for an ENS name:\n\n```bash\ncurl https://api.alpha.ensnode.io/api/resolve/records/nick.eth\n```",".mintlify/docs/ensapi/index.mdx","dc18356fae364a8a",true]